run(sql="
with cte as(
    select * from(
    select guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(appLaunch)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))='2023-02-18'
    union 
    select firstGuid as guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign from `last30Days(sessionSummary)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000))='2023-02-18'
    ) order by guid
)

select case
            
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_APP_D1V_visits'
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d2%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_APP_D2V_visits'
            when (lower(utmContent) not like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) not like '%d2%') and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_APP_D15V_visits'
            
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_msite_D1V_visits'
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d2%' and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_msite_D2V_visits'
            when (lower(utmContent) not like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) not like '%d2%') and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%ftu%' then 'FTU_msite_D15V_visits'
            
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_APP_D1V_visits'
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d2%' and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_APP_D2V_visits'
            when (lower(utmContent) not like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) not like '%d2%') and lower(utmContent) like '%app%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_APP_D15V_visits'
            
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_msite_D1V_visits'
            when lower(utmContent) like '%d2%' and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_msite_D2V_visits'
            when (lower(utmContent) not like '%d1%' and lower(utmContent) not like '%d2%') and lower(utmContent) like '%msite%' and lower(utmContent) like '%rtu%' then 'RTU_msite_D15V_visits'
            
            else 'Others' 
end as Channel, count (distinct sessionId) as visits
from cte
group by Channel
",1000)
